parameters.description: Time vector in years
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Annual time points for model simulation

parameters.description: Sea surface temperature observations
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Observed sea surface temperature in degrees Celsius

parameters.description: Crown-of-thorns larval immigration rate (connectivity between reefs)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Larval immigration rate representing connectivity from upstream reefs (larvae/m²/year)

parameters.description: Adult Crown-of-thorns starfish abundance observations
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Observed adult COTS density (individuals per square meter)

parameters.description: Fast-growing coral (Acropora spp.) cover observations
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Observed fast-growing coral cover percentage

parameters.description: Slow-growing coral (Faviidae and Porites spp.) cover observations
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Observed slow-growing coral cover percentage

parameters.description: Log initial adult COTS density (0.2 individuals/m² untransformed)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log initial condition for adult COTS population density at time zero (individuals/m²). Estimated from data to avoid data leakage.

parameters.description: Log initial fast coral cover (40% untransformed)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log initial condition for fast-growing coral cover at time zero (%). Estimated from data to avoid data leakage.

parameters.description: Log initial slow coral cover (25% untransformed)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log initial condition for slow-growing coral cover at time zero (%). Estimated from data to avoid data leakage.

parameters.description: Log effective fecundity of adult COTS (100 million eggs untransformed, accounting for fertilization success)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log effective egg production per adult COTS female (millions of eggs), accounting for spawning success and fertilization. Literature reports 10-65 million eggs per female, with effective fecundity lower due to fertilization limitations.

parameters.description: Log baseline larval survival rate under poor conditions (0.001 untransformed, most larvae die)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log baseline proportion of COTS larvae surviving to settlement under unfavorable (low nutrient) conditions. Typically 0.0001-0.01 due to high planktonic mortality.

parameters.description: Log strength of nutrient pulse effect on larval survival (10x untransformed, creates episodic outbreaks)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log multiplier for larval survival during favorable nutrient conditions (e.g., flood events, upwelling). Values 5-100x baseline create episodic outbreak dynamics matching GBR observations.

parameters.description: Log SST anomaly threshold for nutrient effect (1.0°C untransformed, negative anomalies indicate upwelling/mixing)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log threshold for SST anomaly to trigger enhanced larval survival. Negative SST anomalies often correlate with nutrient-rich conditions (upwelling, mixing events).

parameters.description: Log rate at which surviving larvae settle to become juveniles (0.001 year⁻¹ untransformed)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log settlement rate from larval to juvenile stage (year⁻¹). Represents successful metamorphosis and attachment to substrate.

parameters.description: Log larval stage mortality rate (2.0 year⁻¹ untransformed, high mortality in plankton)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log mortality rate of COTS larvae in planktonic stage (year⁻¹). High values (1-10 year⁻¹) reflect predation, starvation, and advection losses.

parameters.description: Log baseline COTS recruitment rate from settled juveniles to adults (0.5 year⁻¹ untransformed)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log recruitment rate from juvenile to adult stage per year

parameters.description: Log baseline COTS natural mortality rate (0.5 year⁻¹ untransformed)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log baseline natural mortality rate of adult COTS per year

parameters.description: Log COTS density for Allee effect threshold (0.2 individuals/m² untransformed)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log COTS density threshold for Allee effect (individuals/m²)

parameters.description: Log strength of Allee effect (2.0 untransformed, controls steepness of sigmoid)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log steepness parameter of Allee effect sigmoid function

parameters.description: Log optimal temperature for COTS recruitment (28.5°C untransformed)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log optimal temperature for COTS recruitment (°C)

parameters.description: Log temperature tolerance width for recruitment (2°C untransformed)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log temperature tolerance width for COTS recruitment (°C)

parameters.description: Log density-dependent mortality coefficient (0.2 untransformed)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log density-dependent mortality rate coefficient (m²/individual/year)

parameters.description: Log immigration contribution to larval pool (1.0 untransformed, scales larval connectivity)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log scaling factor for immigration impact on larval pool (represents reef connectivity)

parameters.description: Log fast coral intrinsic growth rate (0.2 year⁻¹ untransformed for Acropora)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log intrinsic growth rate of fast-growing coral (year⁻¹)

parameters.description: Log slow coral intrinsic growth rate (0.04 year⁻¹ untransformed for Porites/Faviidae)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log intrinsic growth rate of slow-growing coral (year⁻¹)

parameters.description: Log fast coral carrying capacity (40% cover untransformed)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log carrying capacity of fast-growing coral cover (%)

parameters.description: Log slow coral carrying capacity (25% cover untransformed)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log carrying capacity of slow-growing coral cover (%)

parameters.description: Log interspecific competition coefficient (0.5 untransformed, symmetric competition)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log interspecific coral competition coefficient (dimensionless)

parameters.description: Log temperature threshold for coral stress (29°C untransformed, bleaching threshold)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log temperature threshold for coral thermal stress (°C)

parameters.description: Log coral mortality rate per degree above threshold (0.2 untransformed)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log coral mortality rate per °C above stress threshold (year⁻¹/°C)

parameters.description: Log COTS attack rate on fast coral (2.0 untransformed, search efficiency)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log COTS attack rate on fast coral (m²/individual/year)

parameters.description: Log COTS attack rate on slow coral (1.0 untransformed, lower than fast coral)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log COTS attack rate on slow coral (m²/individual/year)

parameters.description: Log handling time for fast coral (0.1 years untransformed, time to consume)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log handling time for fast coral consumption (years)

parameters.description: Log handling time for slow coral (0.2 years untransformed, harder to consume)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log handling time for slow coral consumption (years)

parameters.description: Log prey switching threshold (10% cover untransformed, switches when fast coral depleted)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log prey switching threshold coral cover (%)

parameters.description: Log conversion of coral to COTS biomass (0.1 untransformed, assimilation efficiency)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log efficiency converting coral biomass to COTS biomass

parameters.description: Log observation error SD for COTS (0.1 untransformed)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log standard deviation of observation error for COTS density

parameters.description: Log observation error SD for fast coral (3% untransformed)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log standard deviation of observation error for fast coral cover (%)

parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log standard deviation of observation error for slow coral cover (%)
